Square approximation
A good rule of thumb which can be used for mental calculation is the relation

  
    
      
        p
        (
        n
        )
        ≈
        
          
            
              n
              
                2
              
            
            
              2
              m
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle p(n)\approx {\frac {n^{2}}{2m}}}
  which can also be written as

  
    
      
